  "texts": [
    "We divide by the factor B ðnÞ i and subtract t ðnÞ max on both sides of Eq.",
    "(6), which yields:",
    "(7), one can now prove by induction that Eq.",
    "(2) defines an equivalent ReLU network satisfying the identity x ðnÞ i = ðt ðnÞ max À t ðnÞ i Þ=τ c for neurons that fire a spike.",
    "We set x ðnÞ i = 0 for neurons that do not fire a spike in the SNN and note that the rectified linear unit i is in its operating regime"
